---
// WhyPodcast.astro - Sell the value of podcasting (Trust & Authority focus)
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-28 bg-[var(--color-charcoal)]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <p class="text-[var(--color-coral)] text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">
      Why a Podcast?
    </p>

    <!-- Main pitch -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight" data-animate="fade-up">
      People hire experts they trust.
    </h2>

    <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-[var(--color-mist)] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 md:mb-16" data-animate="fade-up">
      A podcast lets them hear your thinking, your voice, your expertise before they ever book a call.
    </p>

    <!-- Mobile: Simple inline list with icons -->
    <div class="md:hidden flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm" data-animate="fade-up">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 text-[var(--color-cream)]">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
        </svg>
        Be Heard
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 text-[var(--color-cream)]">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
        </svg>
        Build Trust
      </span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 text-[var(--color-cream)]">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        Stay Top of Mind
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Desktop: Full three pillars -->
    <div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-animate-stagger>
      <div class="text-center" data-animate-child>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-3">Be Heard</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)]">Share your expertise with thousands instead of one client at a time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center" data-animate-child>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-3">Build Trust</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)]">Prospects hear your voice, your stories, your approach. They show up ready to work with you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center" data-animate-child>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-coral)]/10 border border-[var(--color-coral)]/30 mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-coral)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-3">Stay Top of Mind</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)]">Your podcast works around the clock. Always there when they're ready to buy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
